### ==========================================
### 第21次课 — 文件上传接口测试
### ==========================================
### 前置条件：
### 1. 启动后端服务：mvn spring-boot:run
### 2. 确保 uploads/products/ 目录存在（会自动创建）
### 3. 准备测试图片文件
### ==========================================

### ===== 1. 新增商品（含图片上传） =====

### 1.1 正常新增商品 — 带图片
# @name addProductWithImage
POST http://localhost:8080/api/products/add
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=WebAppBoundary

--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="category"

手机
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="name"

iPhone 16 Pro
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="description"

苹果最新旗舰手机
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="price"

8999
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="brand"

Apple
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="stock"

50
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="isAvailable"

1
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="image"; filename="test.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./test-image.jpg
--WebAppBoundary--

### 1.2 新增商品 — 不带图片（image 字段为空）
# @name addProductWithoutImage
POST http://localhost:8080/api/products/add
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=WebAppBoundary

--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="category"

笔记本
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="name"

MacBook Pro 16
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="price"

19999
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="stock"

30
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="isAvailable"

1
--WebAppBoundary--

### ===== 2. 参数校验失败 =====

### 2.1 缺少必填字段（name 为空）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/products/add
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=WebAppBoundary

--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="category"

手机
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="price"

999
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="stock"

10
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="isAvailable"

1
--WebAppBoundary--

### 2.2 价格为 0
POST http://localhost:8080/api/products/add
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=WebAppBoundary

--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="category"

手机
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="name"

测试商品
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="price"

0
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="stock"

10
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="isAvailable"

1
--WebAppBoundary--

### 2.3 库存为负数
POST http://localhost:8080/api/products/add
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=WebAppBoundary

--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="category"

手机
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="name"

测试商品
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="price"

999
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="stock"

-1
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="isAvailable"

1
--WebAppBoundary--

### 2.4 缺少 isAvailable
POST http://localhost:8080/api/products/add
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=WebAppBoundary

--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="category"

手机
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="name"

测试商品
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="price"

999
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="stock"

10
--WebAppBoundary--

### ===== 3. 访问上传的图片 =====

### 3.1 通过 URL 访问已上传的图片
# 注意：URL 在新增商品响应中返回，此处为示例
GET http://localhost:8080/images/products/{{imageFileName}}

### ===== 4. 原有接口兼容性 =====

### 4.1 获取所有商品（验证图片 URL 字段）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/products

### 4.2 根据 ID 获取商品
GET http://localhost:8080/api/products/1
